    "created_at": "2015-07-23T00:55:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-23T00:55:01Z",
    "body": "Yeah that looks to be quite suspect, especially the `Arc<RefCell<T>>` I'm going to close this because that'd definitely cause this bug to crop up. I'd recommend avoiding `unsafe` code like the plague as much as possible, for example using `RwLock` instead of `RefCell` in this case.\n",
